elements.name: Checking the flight confirmation functionality of the website

steps.name: I am on the home page "http://blazedemo.com/"
I see Welcome to the Simple Travel Ageny! on homePage
I see Choose your departure city and Choose your destination city on page
I am navigated to the "reserve" page
I am navigated to the "purchase" page
I enter the details and click on purchase flight
I am navigated to the "confirmation" page
I should be seeing confirmation id field as not null

name: As a customer I should be able to book flight and get a valid confirmation Id
